description: Resurs Holding AB engages in the provision of banking and financial services. The company is headquartered in Helsingborg, Skane and currently employs 702 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-04-29. The firm offers a wide range of financial services and operates three business segments, namely Payment Solutions, Consumer Loans and Insurance products. The Payment Solutions segment is comprised of retail finance and credit cards. The Consumer Loans segment offers unsecured loans to consumers wishing to finance investments in their home, travels or other consumer goods. Non-life insurance is offered within the Insurance segment under the Solid Forsakring brand.
name: Resurs Holding AB (publ)
